    "created_at": "2016-05-02T03:02:17Z",
    "updated_at": "2016-05-02T03:02:32Z",
    "body": "> At the end, I want to make our software accessible to people who can't afford windows 7+ only.\n\nIs it possible to talk your users into using Xubuntu or Lubuntu?\n\nAnd I am curious if you know exactly how many of your users use XP. If it is a handful it doesn't seem like a good investment of your development time. Especially when Chromium starts stripping XP related code and making XP breaking changes you will have to constantly chase down and patch.\n"
